label: A_cI58_217_ac2g-001
title: $\alpha$-Mn ($A12$) Structure
comments:
This is the ground state structure of manganese.  The high temperature structure, \href{current_web_home_dir/A_cP20_213_cd-001}{$\beta$-Mn ($A13$)}, is stable from 727-1095$^\circ$C and metastable at room temperature (Donohue, 1982). 
 \href{current_web_home_dir/A12B17_cI58_217_g_acg-001}{Mg$_{17}$Al$_{12}$} is a binary form of this structure.
